# **MAIN SHOW**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0802a8e9-a3b9-49e3-b78f-b75041b37ba4/14000.jpg)

*   ## **_ADAM COPELAND AND CHRISTIAN CAGE DEF KIP SABIAN AND KILLSWITCH_**
    

Very fun match that saw Christian trying to avoid Luchasaurus and tagging Edge in without his permission or avoiding extending his arm out too far to get tagged in.

Edge and Christian hit multiple classic double team moves and even some new ones!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f0b3268a-a7be-406a-9ea9-7209c406ca61/14011.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW TNT Championship: Kyle Fletcher def. Hiromu Takahashi_**
    

WHAT A MATCH!!!! Absolute classic from Kyle Fletcher and Takahashi that show Takahashi as a worthy challenger in match with a seemingly obvious conclusion.

Kyle Fletcher continues to make his case for the brightest rising star wrestler in the world today

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/966fce23-4ce4-4cd1-8e57-d7362ab8fa7d/14017.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW TBS CHAMPIONSHIP: Mercedes Moné def. Persiphone, Alex Windsor and Bozilla_**
    

Very good match with tons of innovation. Bozilla will be a star

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/89bcad36-4703-4470-9dbc-bcf5b212ad30/14026.jpg)

"Technical wrestling is like chess... You got a give up a hold to take a hold."

Nigel McGuiness and the legendary Johnny Saint playing chess in a pre match video as Nigel challenges Zack Sabre Jr for the IWGP World Heavyweight Championship

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cf8dbe58-aa13-47ba-a12d-e0fce1a625e9/14030.jpg)

*   ## **_Zack Sabre Jr def. Nigel McGuiness to retain the IWGP World Heavyweight Championship_**
    

What a piece of art, a technical wrestling match that was different from anything else on the card.

The kind of match only Nigel and ZSJ could have provided.

Daniel Garcia had to be warned several times not to get involved or touch the ropes. But he did not turn on Nigel. They hugged instead

