![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/30ff87cf-ead8-487a-8b97-8199756b8017/14071.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW World Championship: Hangman Adam Page def. MJF_**
    

What. A. Match.

MJF tried several times to make Hangman Adam Page disqualify himself. It did not work. At one point, Hangman was actually pinned by MJF for the three count while he had his foot on the rope, the way Mark Briscoe lost a shot at the title.

But this time Briscoe saved Hangman from suffering the same fate.

Hangman gets revenge on MJF by smoking him with the contract behind the refs back and then hitting the Buckshot for the win.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5814720c-65a0-4374-9242-d7bd9f6681f5/14074.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8d27bf7b-eb1d-4f7e-9493-8ccf383fa2b7/14109.jpg)

*   ## **_LIGHTS OUT STEEL CAGE: Will Ospreay, Kenny Omega, Kota Ibushi, Darby Allin and Hiroshi Tanahashi def Death Riders, Young Bucks and Gabe Kidd_**
    

\-WILL OSPREAY GETS A HEROES WELCOME TO FORBIDDEN DOOR AT THE O2 ARENA!!

\-The Young Bucks got their entrance music cut and then MMMBop STARTED PLAYING. This was their first Indy theme music

TABLES, LADDERS AND BEARS, OH MY!!

Another absolute batshit insane match from AEW that must be seen.

Production left a bag of weapons for the Young Bucks under the ring. But it was not thumbtacks.

It was GUMMY BEARS!!!!!! 💀🔥

Jon Moxley put a FORK in Darby Allin's ear lobe.

The babyfaces had to stop TANAHASHI from doing a dive off a cage.

Darby tossed Wheeler Yuta off the cage through the Japanese announce table. THE TABLE DID NOT BREAK!!! El Desparado, who was on commentary, stood there to catch Yuta for some reason and also died.

Darby Allin and Gabe Kidd went from the top of a cage through two tables at ringside!!!!!!!!

What a freaking match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/628d2a5d-2ede-40e6-afd6-58b15eda6143/processed_14114.jpg)

Will Ospreay was left alone in the ring to say goodbye before he leaves for surgery.

But the Death Riders run in, lock the cage and ended Will Ospreay for good.

Several Death Riders DDTs and then a stomped neck through a chair.

Will Ospreay is no more.